These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, country, dubstep, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, brazilian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, scooter, tram
1. the fan of country is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the colombian and the fan of funk##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | dubstep      | country      | disco    |
| Nationality   | thai | japanese | colombian | brazilian |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | tram       | scooter     | trike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapes, plum, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, cooking, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, zombie, western
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
7. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | artichoke     | zucchini     | grapes       | plum    |
| Hobby         | writing | cooking   | collecting | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | zombie | documentary    | animation        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, american, australian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, swimming, skiing, handball
1. the american is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the australian##3
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | lemonade  | cola    | juice |
| Nationality   | australian   | german  | russian  | american    |
| Sport         | swimming    | handball | tennis | skiing  |

