.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, grapes, plum, cabbage
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, disaster, western
4 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, bird, ferret
1. the owner of the frog is between the person watching documentary movies and the person eating watermelon##2
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the hamster is the person eating cabbage##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
7. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | plum   | watermelon     | grapes | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | western | crime   | documentary     |
| Pet           | ferret | bird      | frog     | hamster       |

