.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, banana, radish, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, entrepreneur, journalist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, sports, adventure
1. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
3. the entrepreneur is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the electrician is between the person eating radish and the person eating banana##2
5. the entrepreneur is on the right of the journalist##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
8. the person eating radish is the person watching sports movies##1
9. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | radish      | cucumber | banana      | strawberry |
| Job           | firefighter | electrician | journalist | entrepreneur   |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | adventure   | horror     | crime   |

