.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, chef, lawyer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, r&b, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, handball, ice-hockey, surfing
1. the person who's sport is handball is the engineer##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of disco##1
3. the engineer is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
6. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the chef is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the chef is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | engineer    | chef   | lawyer | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | r&b   | disco         | d&b        |
| Sport         | handball | rugby | ice-hockey         | surfing       |

