.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, woodworking, board-games, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, software-developer, freelancer, fisherman
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, british, turkish, polish
 1. the british is on the left or right of the spanish##3
 2. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the british##3
 4. the freelancer is on the right of the turkish##1
 5. the turkish is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the turkish is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 9. the spanish is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the software-developer is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
11. the software-developer is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | board-games    | skydiving  | woodworking | video-games   |
| Job           | fisherman | software-developer   | freelancer    | lawyer |
| Nationality   | polish      | turkish | british | spanish  |

