1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | blueberry | pumpkin    | cauliflower | eggplant    |
| Hobby         | singing     | camping | skydiving  | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | crime      | documentary   | time-travel         |

