.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, iced-tea, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, electrician, manager, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, ship, airplane
1. the chef is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the electrician##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the manager##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the subway and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person drinking 7up is the electrician##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | 7up   | iced-tea   | tea    | juice |
| Job         | electrician | manager    | engineer      | chef |
| Transport   | subway      | airplane | ship | roller   |

