The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, filmmaking, reading, magic-tricks
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, van, boat, jet-ski
1. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice      | sprite | soy-milk       | lemonade  |
| Hobby       | reading | puzzles | magic-tricks    | filmmaking |
| Transport   | van     | ship         | boat | jet-ski     |

