4. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the train##2
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk    | milk      | mirinda |
| Hobby       | card-games  | singing | traveling | rock-climbing     |
