3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the roller and the person drinking iced-tea##2
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

