4. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
5. the italian is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the thai##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the australian##1
8. the person eating lemon is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
