.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, banana, potato, nectarine
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, teacher, electrician, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, lacrosse, climbing
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person eating carrot and the person eating potato##2
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
8. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | potato | banana  | carrot  | nectarine           |
| Job     | architect | electrician | teacher   | scientist |
| Sport   | climbing   | sailing       | snowboarding | lacrosse  |

 